content: 【ヴィオラドイリー/viola doily】 日本語の紹介ページは下記urlをご覧ください。 * this pattern has a japanese chart and a brief english supplement * this pattern uses these stitchs…slip_stitch chain single_crochet double_crochet treble_crochet 5-double_crochet popcorn fpsc bpdc fptr 5-fpdc popcorn chain-3 picot chain-5 picot * if you work with alize miss batik the size will be 20cm/8 yardage 18-20g/100-110m/110-120yards thanks for watching my pattern
